simulation.agent.variant

Class TotalListener

  • java.lang.Object
    • simulation.agent.variant.TotalListener
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    Agent, Listener, Speaker, VariantAgent

    public class TotalListener
extends java.lang.Object
implements VariantAgent
    A class of variant agents described in "Evolutionary language competition - an agent-based model" paper. Such agents play always roles of listeners in interaction with other agents and their interactions are always successful. Several methods of this class has no effect, but they are necessary so that total listeners can be treated as ordinary agents.
    See Also:
    TotalSpeaker, VariantAgent, ELCPaperSimulationCreator
